name: 03. GLUTTONY
description:
3/7 from "7 Deadly Sins" collection. 

At the farm we have an assigned number for life, you can choose, you can argue, or just sit 
and watch as time passes by. Swallow until your fatigue, believe in those lies that help you through the day. 
Thirst is approaching, I feel tired. The bomb was the key at the perfect time, all I can see is misery, 
more weapons, more war; keep your dreams outside, you wouldn't want to burn again. 
What surrounds us proves to us that there is no way out, not without life; 
and the wait is for those who don't know that out of thoughts you live.

Full story: naranjabrasa.com
